  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- that was next to the-- or he was-- what it was they're called?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] I will- I will-- that-- maybe that will come to me what-- what the name of the street was.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was not far from that--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the next thing was to go to the-- to the partisans.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He arranged already and gave what they're calling this [NON-ENGLISH]?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That is parole?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Parole?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You could say parole, yes?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that I and that Riszik Riszfeld, the father of that son, are going to the partisans.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we came up there, and with that parole, of course.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that commandant from that [NON-ENGLISH]-- from the-- from the partisans there, knows about this already, that we are coming.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I escape.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I escaped.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "During-- that was from the-- from-- from the factory, I already-- when I got this, I was already illegally-- illegal in the-- in the-- in the-- in the-- in Kailis.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was only not existing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there was-- there-- there were already selections done there, too.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Kailis.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's correct.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The tannery?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Who was guard-- guarding me?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Guarding, was only the German-- the people, what they have, with Hanze-- with Martin Hanze on top.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With mine identities.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "With mine.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was mine.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't remember quite rightly what kind of a identity he got.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we got the parole-- the parole, yes, we have just called it?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No-- password.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What's that?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Password is better?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Password.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we came to that Szczerbic.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was the name-- Szczerbic.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's a help of a Polish from the-- outside from the high ranking-- and the kings, and so on.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I beg you?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Szczerbic.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "S-Z-C-Z-E-R-B-I-C.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was the northern part of [NON-ENGLISH] [LAUGHS] The northern part of-- that's in-- close to one of the towns-- [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 21
